models module¶

class models.admintable[source]¶

Bases: object

Model is used to store admin info and has the following atributes 1) user_name 2) Name 3) password

class models.campaign[source]¶

Bases: object

Model is used to store and has the following atributes 1) Subject 2) Owner 3) Description 4) Up Votes 5) Down Votes 6) status

Bases: object

Model is used to store complaints and has the following attributes 1) Subject 2) Owner 3) Description 4) Image

class models.dish[source]¶

Bases: object

Model is used to store dish details and has the following atributes 1) Name 2) Price 3) Description 4) Serving time 5) Image

class models.review[source]¶

Bases: object

Model is used to store food reviews and has the following atributes 1) Owner 2) dish ID 3) Anonumity Status 4) Review Text 5) Review Image

class models.student[source]¶

Bases: object

Model has the following atributes and is used to store student Info 1) ldap ID 2) Name 3) password 4) Verification Code 5) Account Status

class models.waste[source]¶

Bases: object

Model is used to store daily food wastage and has the following atributes 1) Date 2) Total food prepared 3) Wastage
